==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inventor
<hw>In*vent"or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.: cf. F.
<ets>inventeur</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who invents or finds out something
new; a contriver; especially, one who invents mechanical devices, new
drugs, new processes, or other useful objects or procedures.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inventorial</ent>⟦br⟧
